{"tid":1897172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民政事務署：黃色、黑色口罩唔撥款俾你班契弟買","createTime":"2020-02-25T14:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T15:37:36.000Z","uid":3513,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"60b9479b99fda20d0e638fba30c5a7554109b123","tid":1897172,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"不過，他批評民政署不但拖延處理撥款，又要求團體派口罩之餘亦要做到不要令人群聚集，日前更接獲通知，指要跟隨政府物流署購買外科口罩的規定選購口罩，當中口罩列明只能屬綠色、藍色、白色、粉紅色或紫色。<br />\n負責人稱，他們早前打算選購的口罩正正是黃色，但因被民政署警告，若不按照規定，將不獲發放撥款，故只有放棄，「之前搵到一批由美國入口嘅黃色口罩，價錢比較平同質素唔差，本來買到10萬個，但而家因為咁無得買嗰批，暫時只買到8萬個。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200225/JBCJEYKVGPTA6OIIXQUEGDK4WY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200225%2FJBCJEYKVGPTA6OIIXQUEGDK4WY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=e60af8e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200225%2FJBCJEYKVGPTA6OIIXQUEGDK4WY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=f52fba17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200225/JBCJEYKVGPTA6OIIXQUEGDK4WY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點撚解林鄭仲有9% 支持？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"3892b40224f9985540dcde7f3cba90176f36d49e","tid":1897172,"uid":3513,"like":5,